thread.title: Tata Motors Says Feb Domestic Sales of Commercial Vehicles Up about 36 Pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Tata Motors Says Feb Domestic Sales of Commercial Vehicles Up about 36 Pct
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - Tata Motors Ltd:
* SAYS FEB DOMESTIC COMMERCIAL VEHICLE SALES OF 41,222 UNITS VERSUS 30,407 UNITS LAST YEAR
* SAYS FEB DOMESTIC PASSENGER VEHICLE SALES OF 17,771 UNITS VERSUS 12,272 UNITS LAST YEAR
* SAYS FEB SALES FROM EXPORTS WERE 4,768 UNITS, DOWN 3 PERCENT
* SAYS FEB DOMESTIC SALES OF TATA COMMERCIAL AND PASSENGER VEHICLES OF 58,993 UNITS VERSUS 42,679 UNITS LAST YEAR Source text: bit.ly/2F3VutI
